WE COMMIT TO MAKE YOU ECO-FIT


A long range of eco-friendly yoga & fitness accessories to simplify your fitness goals no matter where your impromptu travel plans take you.

A durable & light-weight Premium Yoga Mat made of natural Jute Fibers & PER Polymer Environmental Resin that has a textured surface for Superior Grip, Jute Eco Yoga, Pilates & Exercise Yoga mats are made of 100% raw materials & has antimicrobial properties for extra-sweaty practices. The mat can also be used for Pilates and floor exercises.

Exhale the past and inhale the future on customized yoga mats, beautifully designed with your own choice of pictures & images only at Maji Sports!

Our Fitness & Muscle Recovery Travel bundles are a great way for you to incorporate a compact and diverse set of workout into your fitness routine whether you practice Yoga, Pilates, HIIT, CrossFit, Spinning, Tennis, Boxing, Dance or Running.
